title: VA Class IV WTS
name: VA Class IV WTS
description: These data represent the Virginia Department of Game and Inland Fisheries (VDGIF) coldwater or trout, streams. The Fisheries Division of VDGIF has identified all of the reaches in this dataset as wild (Class I-IV) or stockable (Class V and VI) trout streams or as tributaries to wild trout streams. These classifications give the streams special management considerations and protection. Please note that many of the streams are on private property and are not necessarily public fishing waters.

author.source: Virginia Department of Game and Inland Fisheries (VDGIF)
